
    THE BRUTAL murder of an 80-year-old man on Christmas day
has left a village in southern Uganda reeling in shock.According to Daily
Monitor, Joseph Sonko was brutally attacked in his home in Byabuku village
in Buikwe District.The motive for the attack was unclear, but the report
states that the madala’s body was chopped into pieces. His head, hands,
